      "id": "PopularPost367304",
      "post_content": "I've been running [Wild Guess](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Guess) in a burn deck alongside [Guttersnipe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Guttersnipe), [Young Pyromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Young Pyromancer), and a [Squee, Goblin Nabob](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squee, Goblin Nabob) or two (Doesn't help you much for standard, but its great in Modern); if you don't have flashback, madness or other ways to dredge up your graveyard Squee is a great choice to circumvent the \"net-loss\" of cards caused by Wild Guess.",
      "posted_by": "WarmasterGibbon",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost367304\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I've been running <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wild Guess\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Guess\">Wild Guess</a> in a burn deck alongside <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Guttersnipe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Guttersnipe\">Guttersnipe</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Young Pyromancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Young Pyromancer\">Young Pyromancer</a>, and a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Squee, Goblin Nabob\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squee, Goblin Nabob\">Squee, Goblin Nabob</a> or two (Doesn't help you much for standard, but its great in Modern); if you don't have flashback, madness or other ways to dredge up your graveyard Squee is a great choice to circumvent the \"net-loss\" of cards caused by Wild Guess.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '367304'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy106670\">WarmasterGibbon</span>\r\n                                (3/11/2014 7:17:42 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n              